<SLUG> BC-CAMPAIGN-PLATFORMS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FOR ACTIVISTS, NAILING THESES TO THEIR PARTY'S DOORS 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
only. Asian and European points: Call Karl Horwitz in Paris for
